It's the PERSON not the toon that your dealing with. I almost never have a problem getting agro off any pally or SK I hunt with. When I do have a problem, it's because the SK or Pally wants to tank, and CAN tank. I trust my main SKs enough to make that choice, and if they wanna tank a couple, thats' cool. But that's only in groups, and the SKs I hunt with could tank PoV critters. Heck, half the time when in ToV and breaking the hallway I'll have a SK or Pally tank the add. <br>
